                                       </math> of real numbers is called decreasing if <math>
                                          <latex>a_n\geq a_{n+1}</latex>
                                       </math> for all <math>
                                          <latex>n\in \NNr</latex>
                                       </math>.</para.body>
                                 </para>
                              </info>
                           </index.glossary>
                           <index.glossary>
                              <term>sequence</term>
                              <term>decreasing</term>
                              <info>
                                 <para>
                                    <para.body>A sequence <math>
                                          <latex>(a_n)</latex>
                                       </math> of real numbers is called decreasing if <math>
                                          <latex>a_n\geq a_{n+1}</latex>
                                       </math> for all <math>
                                          <latex>n\in \NNr</latex>
                                       </math>.</para.body>
                                 </para>
                              </info>
                           </index.glossary>
                           <index.glossary>
                              <term>monotone</term>
                              <term>sequence</term>
                              <info>
                                 <para>
                                    <para.body>A sequence <math>
                                          <latex>(a_n)</latex>
                                       </math> of real numbers is called monotone if it is increasing or decreasing.</para.body>
                                 </para>
                              </info>
                           </index.glossary>
                           <index.glossary>
                              <term>sequence</term>
                              <term>monotone</term>
                              <info>
                                 <para>
                                    <para.body>A sequence <math>
                                          <latex>(a_n)</latex>
                                       </math> of real numbers is called monotone if it is increasing or decreasing.</para.body>
                                 </para>
                              </info>
                           </index.glossary>
                        </para>
                     </li>
                     <li>
