                              <info>
                                 <para>
                                    <para.body>A sequence <math>
                                          <latex>(a_n)</latex>
                                       </math> of real numbers is called strictly increasing if <math>
                                          <latex> a_n &lt; a_{n+1} </latex>
                                       </math> for all <math>
                                          <latex>n\in \NNr</latex>
